Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:59.59,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}囁く天使は堕ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:06.69,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しく食むわ　あなたの全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:11.89,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
